{"tid":1807484,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"十大屋苑全年價量齊升　共2262宗升8%","createTime":"2020-01-02T00:16:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-02T09:28:21.000Z","uid":81228,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fdd5fe26a181f5dd5d3b55cfc93e05b9d7241e35","tid":1807484,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T00:16:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20200101/s00064/a4ac932897fd286f37f9c05d4a7bd06a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20200101%2Fs00064%2Fa4ac932897fd286f37f9c05d4a7bd06a.jpg&h=021437e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【明報專訊】回顧2019年全年，本港十大屋苑共錄得2262宗成交，較2018年2094宗上升8%，當中嘉湖山莊去年累計錄得439宗，與前年相若，交投量再次榮登十大屋苑之首；呎價方面，有8個屋苑2019年全年成交呎價錄得介乎1.7%至13.8%升幅，故去年十大屋苑中，大部分屋苑均價量齊升。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>上月起價量齊跌</strong><br />\n<br />\n據中原統計，十大屋苑成交量2019年最高首3位，順次序為嘉湖山莊、沙田第一城及太古城。同時，有8個屋苑去年呎價錄得按年增長，惟東涌映灣園及紅磡黃埔花園的呎價則錄得1.6%及2.1%的跌幅。不過，12月整體二手交投放緩，十大屋苑亦現價量齊跌迹象，2019年12月錄118宗成交，較11月158宗下跌約25%，但仍為自去年9月以來，連續4個月錄得破百宗成交。成交呎價則出現下調，共有7個屋苑呎價錄得0.9%至4.9%跌幅，僅太古城、黃埔花園、新都城按月成交呎價則靠穩。<br />\n<br />\n其他二手成交方面，新近入伙的北角維港頌有2房銀主盤於二手市場沽出。香港置業分行營業經理陳偉業表示，維港頌6座高層D室，實用面積565方呎，2房間隔，享海景，由銀主以1650萬元放售，新近以1651萬元成交，實呎29,221元。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>維港頌銀主盤　兩年半僅升1.7萬</strong><br />\n<br />\n原業主於2017年5月以1649.3萬元購入，當時獲發展商旗下財務公司提供第一按揭，惟因斷供而遭財務公司收樓淪為銀主盤，現時成交價僅較兩年半前僅高1.7萬元或0.1%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F/article/20200101/s00004/1577817784940/%E5%8D%81%E5%A4%A7%E5%B1%8B%E8%8B%91%E5%85%A8%E5%B9%B4%E5%83%B9%E9%87%8F%E9%BD%8A%E5%8D%87-%E5%85%B12262%E5%AE%97%E5%8D%878\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25BF%259F%2Farticle%2F20200101%2Fs00004%2F1577817784940%2F%25E5%258D%2581%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25B1%258B%25E8%258B%2591%25E5%2585%25A8%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2583%25B9%25E9%2587%258F%25E9%25BD%258A%25E5%258D%2587-%25E5%2585%25B12262%25E5%25AE%2597%25E5%258D%25878&d=navV%2BA4%2FMRIetR8KyPOOANHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=aadff379\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25BF%259F%2Farticle%2F20200101%2Fs00004%2F1577817784940%2F%25E5%258D%2581%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25B1%258B%25E8%258B%2591%25E5%2585%25A8%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2583%25B9%25E9%2587%258F%25E9%25BD%258A%25E5%258D%2587-%25E5%2585%25B12262%25E5%25AE%2597%25E5%258D%25878&h=7800f84d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F/article/20200101/s00004/1577817784940/%E5%8D%81%E5%A4%A7%E5%B1%8B%E8%8B%91%E5%85%A8%E5%B9%B4%E5%83%B9%E9%87%8F%E9%BD%8A%E5%8D%87-%E5%85%B12262%E5%AE%97%E5%8D%878</a>"},{"pid":"620f5ece5376fab9dbe2235387525779615a0861","tid":1807484,"uid":162526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T05:15:52.000Z","msg":"高成交咁跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b61ebab5b3e6d5b7f307e15204773b4fb2e0e217","tid":1807484,"uid":89538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T09:07:22.000Z","msg":"頭半年做埋後半年生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88e62e7f239c9cff1f482e4bebdd6064433135db","tid":1807484,"uid":100256,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T09:28:21.000Z","msg":"說好的樓市死亡漩渦呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}